{"tid":2184483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英澳護照持有人有望1月1號起自由工作居留","createTime":"2020-09-01T14:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T10:11:43.000Z","uid":305299,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"372a707c3ccd292de74708a1b87f36aef3b42bd0","tid":2184483,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9xnSoAb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9xnSoAb.jpg&h=eb3d4b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國聘請咗前任澳洲總理 Tony Abbott 出任英國貿易委員會主席，而依位前任澳洲總理 Tony Abbott 就表示，希望本月兩國討論脫歐後貿易協議入面，加入自由行動協議，允許兩國人民於對方國家自由工作居留，互認對方標準及專業資格，並希望於明年1月1號就生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，依位前任澳洲總理 Tony Abbott同現任澳洲執政黨同屬一個政黨，都係澳洲自由黨，相信有利貿易談判<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果順利落實自由行動協議嘅話，長遠對 BNO 持有人及其家屬都會有利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cityam.com/tony-abbott-uk-australia-freedom-of-movement-could-begin-on-1-january/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityam.com%2Ftony-abbott-uk-australia-freedom-of-movement-could-begin-on-1-january%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=076e09c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cityam.com/tony-abbott-uk-australia-freedom-of-movement-could-begin-on-1-january/</a>"},{"pid":"939f0182d6b23ac50d71ee5008a0c1d00035f397","tid":2184483,"uid":78785,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"我係bc 但平一直想去澳洲<br />\n<br />\n機會來了！"},{"pid":"6cb1346676efb3e79544fb39d7fa3561c7050e11","tid":2184483,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"CANZUK！"},{"pid":"58ad9a105bf0f0ed0c6ba54b858cb475f5451e54","tid":2184483